==&quot;Let&#x27;s Get Together with Hayley Mills&quot;==
Let&#x27;s Get Together with Hayley Mills, released in 1962, was Mills&#x27; only solo album. It had the million-selling song &quot;Let&#x27;s Get Together&quot; and &quot;Johnny Jingo&quot;. 

