# &quot;Cobbler Cobbler&quot; – 2:14
# &quot;Johnny Jingo&quot; – 1:38
# &quot;Pollyanna Song&quot; – 1:57
# &quot;Jimmie Bean&quot; – 1:53
# &quot;Let&#x27;s Get Together&quot; – 1:29

